hits.definition:
阳 (F 陽)

[yáng] opposite of 阴 yīn;

    太阳 tàiyáng the sun

整

[zhěng] (= 整个 zhěnggè) whole;

    调整 tiáozhěng adjust;

    整齐 zhěngqí neat

支

[zhī] branch, support;

    支持 zhīchí sustain;

    地支 dìzhī the Twelve Terrestrial Branches

古

[gǔ] (= 古代 gǔdài) ancient

{Compare with 舌 shé tongue}

汉 (F 漢)

[hàn] Chinese ethnicity;

    汉语 hànyu Chinese;

    汉字 hànzi Chinese character;

    老汉 lǎohàn old man

突

[tū] charge forward, stick out;

    突然 tūrán suddenly

选 (F 選)

[xuǎn] (= 选择 xuǎnzé) choose, select;

    选举 xuǎnjǔ election

刊

[kān] periodical, publication;

    报刊 bǎokān periodical publications, the press

亚 (F 亞)

[yà] inferior, second;

    亚洲 Yàzhōu Asia

伤 (F 傷)

[shāng] wound, injury, injure;

    创伤 chuāngshāng trauma

类 (F 類)

[lèi] category, kind, type;

    类似 lèisì similar

备 (F 備)

[bèi] (= 准备 zhǔnbèi) get ready, prepare;

    设备 shèbèi equipment
